《'''未来世界'''》（{{lang-en|''The Shape of Things to Come''}}）是[[美国电视|美国]]电视剧《[[迷失|迷失]]》[[迷失_(第四季)|第4季]]的第9集，也是全剧的[[迷失剧集列表|第81集]]，于2008年4月24日通过[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]在美国首播，还通过[[CTV电视网|CTV电视网]]在加拿大[[首演|首播]]<ref>{{cite web | work = [[美国广播公司|ABC]] Medianet | date = 2008-02-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140723171542/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=022008_01 | deadurl = yes | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=022008_01 | title = ABC Announces the Return of Television's Biggest Hits Shows | accessdate = 2014-07-23 | archivedate = 2014-07-23}}</ref>。本集的剧本由[[执行制作人|执行制作人]]德鲁·高达和[[制作人|制作人]]布莱恩·{{lang|en|K}}·沃恩在2008年2月上旬共同创作完成，另一名执行制作人斯蒂芬·威廉姆斯[[杰克·本德|杰克·本德]]于3月中旬[[导演|执导]]<ref>{{cite web | work = ABC Medianet | date = 2008-04-07 | archivedate = 2012-02-10 | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=040708_14 | title = Locke's Camp Comes Under Attack and Jack Attempts to Identify a Body That Washes Ashore | accessdate = 2012-02-10 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120210143046/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=040708_14}}</ref>。节目剧情围绕[[本杰明·莱纳斯|本杰明·莱纳斯]]（[[迈克尔·爱默生|迈克尔·爱默生]]饰）展开，他和[[海洋航空|海洋航空]]815航班空难幸存者于2004年12月在兵营受到攻击，剧中的未来闪影剧情发生在2005年下半年，显示本招募[[萨伊德·贾拉|萨伊德·贾拉]]充当杀手来对付敌人查尔斯·威德摩尔。

《未来世界》是《迷失》中为数不多的几集包含[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]以外地区取景镜头的剧集之一。这集节目本来是第4季第2批剧集的第1集，原计划这批会连续播放至第4季结束。但受为期100天的[[2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工|2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工]]影响，《迷失》的制作被迫中止，编剧也停止为第4季后半季继续创作，节目停播4周后才恢复<ref>{{cite news | last = Nichols | first = Katherine | date = 2008-04-22 | url = http://archives.starbulletin.com/2008/04/22/features/story01.html | title = The Dirt on 'Lost' | newspaper = ''Honolulu Star-Bulletin'' | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | archivedate = 2015-09-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150907194856/http://archives.starbulletin.com/2008/04/22/features/story01.html | deadurl = no}}</ref>。本集首播一共吸引了1400万美国观众收看，并获得评论界好评。多位评论家称赞爱默生演技精湛，特别是本看到养女[[艾莉克斯·卢梭|艾莉克斯]]遭处决后的反应。他因这集演出获[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]提名，剧集本身也获得了一项提名<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Academy of Television Arts & Sciences | accessdate = 2009-09-08 | date = 2008-07-17 | url = http://cdn.emmys.tv/awards/2008pte/60thpte_noms.php | title = Complete 2008 Nominations List | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090908033316/http://cdn.emmys.tv/awards/2008pte/60thpte_noms.php | archivedate = 2009-09-08}}</ref>。

== 剧情 ==
本集剧情发生在2004年12月27日，距[[大洋航空815号班机空难|大洋航空815号班机空难]]已经过了97天。“卡哈纳号”（{{lang|en|Kahana}}）货轮上雷医生的尸体被冲到空难幸存者露营的海滩上。[[丹尼尔·法拉第|丹尼尔·法拉第]]（[[杰瑞米·戴维斯|杰瑞米·戴维斯]]饰）用[[摩尔斯电码|摩尔斯电码]]联系货轮，询问雷医生到底出了什么事。得到回音后，丹尼尔声称货轮很快就会派营救直升机到岛上来，但[[柏纳·纳德勒|柏纳·纳德勒]]发现他在说谎，原来船上的真实回复是：“你说什么呢？医生他很好啊。”[[杰克·谢泼德|杰克·谢泼德]]（[[马修·福克斯|马修·福克斯]]饰）虽然已在胃痛的折磨下熬了一整天，但他还是逼迫丹尼尔吐露实情，货轮根本就没有营救岛上幸存者的打算<ref name="episode">{{cite episode | credits = Vaughan, Brian K. (writer) & Goddard, Drew (writer) & [[杰克·本德|Bender, Jack]] (director) | title = The Shape of Things to Come | series = ''[[迷失|Lost]]'' | network = ABC | number = [[迷失剧集列表|9]] | season = [[迷失_(第四季)|4]] | airdate = 2008-04-24}}</ref>。

与此同时，[[艾莉克斯·卢梭|艾莉克斯]]被货轮上的[[马丁·克米|马丁·克米]]（[[凯文·杜兰|凯文·杜兰]]）等人所擒<ref>{{cite episode | credits = Sarnoff, Elizabeth (writer) & Vaughan, Brian K. (writer) & Williams, Stephen (director) | title = [[故友重逢|Meet Kevin Johnson]] | series = Lost  | network = ABC | number = 8 | season = 4 | airedate = 2008-03-20}}</ref>。这些人押着她前去兵营，艾莉克斯设法拉响警报，告诉[[本杰明·莱纳斯|本杰明·莱纳斯]]等人有敌人到来。本、[[约翰·洛克_(迷失)|约翰·洛克]]（[[特瑞·欧奎恩|特瑞·欧奎恩]]饰）、[[休戈·「赫利」·瑞斯|休戈·「赫利」·瑞斯]]（[[乔治·加西亚|乔治·加西亚]]饰）以本的房子设防，[[詹姆斯·「索耶」·福特|詹姆斯·「索耶」·福特]]（[[乔什·哈洛威|乔什·哈洛威]]饰）则前去指示兵营内的其他幸存者撤离。[[克莱尔·李特顿|克莱尔·李特顿]]（[[艾蜜莉·迪瑞文|艾蜜莉·迪瑞文]]）的屋子被炸并起火，幸得索耶救援才幸免于难，但还是有另外3个幸存者被押着艾莉克斯前来的雇佣兵枪杀。克米找到[[麦尔斯·斯特劳姆|麦尔斯·斯特劳姆]]（[[肯·梁|肯·梁]]饰），然后给他一台[[无线对讲机|无线对讲机]]去拿给本。本拿过对讲机，克米要求他投降，否则就杀掉艾莉克斯。本想要谈判，但却看到克米直接枪杀了艾莉克斯。震惊之下，本喃喃自语说对方违反了规则，然后走进房里的密室并把自己锁在里面，然后通过某种方式召唤出黑烟怪物。怪物出现后向克米及其他雇佣兵发起攻击，片刻间就解决了所有敌人。其他人逃离树林，本则独自跪在艾莉克斯的尸体旁，表现得非常伤心。之后，本和洛克一起去找[[迷失角色列表|雅各布]]，希望能获得进一步指示。索耶、赫利、克莱尔和亚伦则打算和麦尔斯一起返回海滩，但洛克不同意，要求之前找到过雅各布木屋的赫利和自己一同上路，面对洛克的枪口，赫利只能从命<ref name="episode" /><ref>{{cite episode | credits = [[戴蒙·林道夫|Lindelof, Damon]] (writer) & Cuse, Carlton (writer) & Bender, Jack (director) | title = [[结局的开始|The Beginning of the End]] | series = Lost  | network = ABC | number = 1 | season = 4 | airedate = 2008-01-31}}</ref>。

剧情插入未来闪影桥段，本身穿冬装在[[撒哈拉沙漠|撒哈拉沙漠]]醒来，上臂还有条长长的刀口。遇到两个持枪当地人的挑衅后，本杀死其中一人并将另一人打昏，然后骑马前往[[突尼西亚|突尼西亚]]的[[托泽尔|托泽尔]]，原来这时已经是2005年10月24日。接下来本又来到[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]的[[提克里特|提克里特]]，[[萨伊德·贾拉|萨伊德·贾拉]]的夫人纳迪娅已经去世，这里正举行葬礼。本告诉萨伊德，是查尔斯·威德摩尔命令伊斯梅尔·巴克尔杀害纳迪娅。在本的诱使下，巴克尔落入圈套，萨伊德杀死他后还在继续朝尸体开枪。萨伊德接受本的招募，成为他手下的杀手。本前往伦敦并闯进威德摩尔的豪宅，虽然没能杀掉威德摩尔，但他威胁会杀死威德摩尔的女儿来为艾莉克斯报仇。威德摩尔则称，总有一天他会从本手里夺回那座岛<ref name="episode" />。

== 制作 ==
[[File:Dharka.jpg|thumb]]
美国编剧协会于2007年11月4日开始罢工<ref>{{cite news | last1 = McNary | first1 = Dave | last2 = Littleton | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141120230434/http://variety.com/2007/biz/news/writers-call-for-strike-1117975256/ | deadurl = no | first2 = Cynthia | date = 2007-11-02 | url = http://variety.com/2007/biz/news/writers-call-for-strike-1117975256/ | title = Writers Call for Strike | work = ''[[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]]'' | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | archivedate = 2014-11-20}}</ref>，这时《迷失》第4季原计划的16集中还只有8集的剧本已经完成<ref>{{cite web | last1 = Lindelof | first1 = Damon | last2 = Cuse | first2 = Carlton | date = 2007-11-05 | title = "Lost" writers: "Like putting down a 'Harry Potter' book in the middle" | url = http://variety.com/2007/biz/news/lost-writers-like-putting-down-a-harry-potter-book-in-the-middle-25959/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150120055616/http://variety.com/2007/biz/news/lost-writers-like-putting-down-a-harry-potter-book-in-the-middle-25959/ | archivedate = 2015-01-20 | deadurl = no | work = ''Variety'' | accessdate = 2015-09-14}}</ref>，这8集分别于2008年1至3月播映<ref>{{cite news | last = Grossman | first = Ben | date = 2007-11-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071228101351/http://www.broadcastingcable.com/article/CA6498735.html?industryid=47168 | url = http://www.broadcastingcable.com/article/CA6498735.html?industryid=47168 | title = Strike Coverage: ABC to Air Partial Season of ''Lost'' | work = Broadcasting & Cable | archivedate = 2007-12-28 | accessdate = 2007-12-28 }}</ref>。罢工于2008年2月12日结束，接下来编剧们意识到余下的时间只够再制作5集，不过其中的第5集之后又扩充成了两集<ref>{{cite web | last = Ausiello | first = Michael | work = ''TV Guide'' | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | date = 2008-04-11 | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/its-official-lost-8140/ | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714145911/http://www.tvguide.com/news/its-official-lost-8140.aspx | title = It's Official: Lost Finds Extra Hour… But There's a Twist!}}</ref>。为此，编剧们开始将原计划拍成8集的剧情压缩成6集<ref>{{cite news | last = Levin | work = ''USA Today'' | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | first = Gary | date = 2008-02-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020203222/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2008-02-11-strike-production_N.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2008-02-11-strike-production_N.htm | title = Television Production Goes from Stalled to High Gear | archivedate = 2012-10-20 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，还有部分内容则会纳入[[迷失_(第五季)|第5季]]<ref name="ugo">{{cite web | last = Lachonis | first = Jon "DocArzt" | date = 2008-05-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080531015804/http://www.ugo.com/ugo/html/gallery/default.asp?gallery=yunjin_kim_filmtv | url = http://www.ugo.com/tv/lost/?cur=darlton | title = Damon Lindelof and Carlton Cuse | work = UGO Networks | accessdate = 2008-05-31 | archivedate = 2008-05-31 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。[[执行制作人|执行制作人]]兼首席编剧[[戴蒙·林道夫|戴蒙·林道夫]]表示：“我们（仍然）会执行第4季的全部剧情方案。对此（我们）只需要把高效率的剧情发展转变成超高效率即可。这并不需要临时抱佛脚，只要稍微用点力去踩油门就可以了……所以请拿稳你的帽子……不过，那些对[[权真秀|权真秀]]（[[金大贤|金大贤]]饰）和赫利的乒乓球比赛期待已久的观众就会非常失望了。”<ref>{{cite web | last = Dos Santos | accessdate = 2008-04-23 | first = Kristin | date = 2008-02-13 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080423142109/http://www.eonline.com/gossip/kristin/detail/index.jsp?uuid=cde3739d-0729-45c2-b6bd-9b28c9f3a06d | title = The Return of ''Mother'', ''Life'' and, Oh Yeah, ''Lost'' | publisher = E! | archivedate = 2008-04-23 | url = http://www.eonline.com/gossip/kristin/detail/index.jsp?uuid=cde3739d-0729-45c2-b6bd-9b28c9f3a06d}}</ref>众编剧表示希望《未来世界》作为本季的第2批剧集播出<ref>{{cite news | last = Albiniak | first = Paige | date = 2008-02-24 | url = http://nypost.com/2008/02/24/10-reasons-why-lost-is-found/ | title = Ten Reasons Why 'Lost' is Found | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131009035109/http://nypost.com/2008/02/24/10-reasons-why-lost-is-found/ | newspaper = ''[[纽约邮报|New York Post]]'' | accessdate = 2015-09-14 | archivedate = 2013-10-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，但美国广播公司没有同意，而是将这集作为季中的首播剧集。编剧们还发现，这次大罢工也带来一些好处，一些演员原本参演的节目因罢工取消，所以能够腾出档期出演《迷失》，同时编剧们也有了时间来解答观众的疑问<ref>{{cite news | last = Jensen | first = Jeff "Doc" | date = 2008-02-22 | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2008/02/29/writers-strike-postscripts | title = Writers' Strike Postscripts | work = ''[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]'' | accessdate = 2015-09-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150203213918/http://www.ew.com/article/2008/02/29/writers-strike-postscripts | archivedate = 2015-02-03}}</ref>。他们之后还称，在这次罢工的影响下，第4季实际上比原计划更为优秀，因为他们能够将其中略嫌疲软、烦杂的内容去除，而且罢工也让他们得到充分的休息，得以在最后6集中投入饱满的精力<ref>{{cite web | last = Dos Santos | first = Kristin | date = 2008-05-09 | url = http://www.eonline.com/news/13448/news | title = Is Claire Dead? Are They Really Time Traveling? Lost's Bosses Speak! | publisher = E! | accessdate = 2015-09-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150914162943/http://www.eonline.com/news/13448/news | archivedate = 2015-09-14}}</ref>。《迷失》的前3季都是周三晚在美国和加拿大播出<ref>{{cite web | last = Dos Santos | first = Kristin | date = 2007-12-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150914164114/http://www.eonline.com/news/4027/lost-it-s-baaack | archivedate = 2015-09-14 | url = http://www.eonline.com/news/4027/lost-it-s-baaack | title = ''Lost'': It's Baaack! | publisher = E! | accessdate = 2015-09-15 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，第4季在罢工前是于周四晚21点播出，这一时段通常都是由《[[实习医生格蕾|实习医生格蕾]]》占据 <ref>{{cite web | last = Martell | first = Erin | date = 2008-02-13 | url = http://www.tvsquad.com/2008/02/13/second-batch-of-lost-episodes-will-follow-greys-anatomy | title = Second Batch of ''Lost'' Episodes Will Follow ''Grey's Anatomy'' | work = ''TV Squad'' | accessdate = 2011-05-21 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110521150913/http://www.tvsquad.com/2008/02/13/second-batch-of-lost-episodes-will-follow-greys-anatomy/ | archivedate = 2011-05-21}}</ref>，但《未来世界》开始和之后的3集都调整到周四晚22点播出，排在《实习医生格蕾》播映之后<ref>{{cite web | last = Ausiello | first = Michael | date = 2008-02-13 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/exclusive-lost-finds-8317/ | title = Exclusive: Lost Finds Post-Grey's Berth! | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714151340/http://www.tvguide.com/news/exclusive-lost-finds-8317.aspx | work = ''TV Guide'' | accessdate = 2015-09-15 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

《未来世界》的编剧工作于2008年2至3月同《回家真好》（{{lang|en|''There's No Place Like Home''}}）和《[[林中木屋_(迷失)|林中木屋]]》（{{lang|en|''Cabin Fever''}}）一起进行<ref name="ugo" />。本集剧名源自[[赫伯特·乔治·威尔斯|赫伯特·乔治·威尔斯]]1933年的[[未来世界_(小说)|同名科幻小说]]<ref name="podcast">{{cite video | last1 = Lindelof | first1 = Damon | last2 = Cuse | first2 = Carlton | date = 2008-04-25 | url = http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/LOST_410_audio_podcast_aaf44dbb-c51c-4fe8-babf-e80bcbd3c792_1643855.mp3 | title = Official ''Lost'' Audio Podcast | publisher = ABC | accessdate = 2012-02-10 | archivedate = 2012-02-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120210185753/http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/LOST_410_audio_podcast_aaf44dbb-c51c-4fe8-babf-e80bcbd3c792_1643855.mp3 | deadurl = yes | format = MP3}}</ref>。执行制作人兼编剧德鲁·高达（{{lang|en|Drew Goddard}}）称，本集可能是他参与制作的《迷失》中最喜欢的一集，他也对能够参与这些剧集的制作深感幸运<ref>{{cite web | last = Dos Santos | first = Kristin | date = 2008-03-21 | url = http://www.eonline.com/news/17894/lost-redux-if-loathing-ben-is-wrong-i-don-t-wanna-be-right | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080802050013/http://www.eonline.com/gossip/kristin/detail/index.jsp?uuid=0699b3ce-6e96-4a14-9781-bbc43e289137 | title = ''Lost'' Redux: If Loathing Ben Is Wrong, I Don't Wanna Be Right | publisher = E! | accessdate = 2015-09-15 | archivedate = 2008-08-02}}</ref>。节目于3月10日开拍，3月25日收工<ref>{{cite news | last = Gordon | first = Mike | title = 'Lost' going back into film action here on March 10 | newspaper = ''Honolulu Advertiser'' | date = 2008-02-29 | url = http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2008/Feb/29/ln/hawaii802290369.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714221624/http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2008/Feb/29/ln/hawaii802290369.html | accessdate = 2015-09-15 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-07-14}}</ref>。男演员阿兰·戴尔（{{lang|en|Alan Dale}}）需要参与舞台剧《[[火腿骑士|火腿骑士]]》（{{lang|en|''Spamalot''}}）的拍摄，无法飞去[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]，因此本和威德摩尔对质的镜头实际上是在伦敦取景，多名剧组成员和爱默生一起飞抵伦敦拍摄这场戏<ref name="podcast" />。剧组之前已经拍好了一组克莱尔看到未来事件的镜头，但这段内容因节目时间上的压缩而被剪<ref name="ew">{{cite news|last=Jensen |first=Jeff "Doc" |date=2008-04-25 |url=http://www.ew.com/recap/lost-recap-ben-unleashed |title=''Lost'' recap: Ben unleashed |work=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2015-09-15 |archivedate=2014-02-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140224203617/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20195369_2%2C00.html |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

第4季早期的剧集中有3名幸存者跟随洛克一起前往兵营，其中1人名叫道格（{{lang|en|Doug}}），由肖恩·道格拉斯·霍本（{{lang|en|Sean Douglas Hoban}}）饰演，他之前曾在[[试播_(迷失)|试播集]]中出演“4号乘客”，本集是他的名字首次出现在演员名单上。霍本还曾充当前3季重要角色[[查理·佩斯|查理·佩斯]]扮演者[[多米尼克·莫纳汉|多米尼克·莫纳汉]]的特技替身。<ref>{{cite news|last=Snierson |first=Dan |date=2007-05-24 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20040051_2,00.html |title=The Q&A: Sorry, Charlie |work=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2014-08-18 |archivedate=2014-08-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819154529/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20040051_2%2C00.html |deadurl=yes }}</ref>霍本在《未来世界》中有一句台词，为此他还必须参加试镜，同其他多位演员竞争<ref>{{cite web|last=McPherson |first=Sam |date=2008-06-22 |url=http://lostpedia.wikia.com/wiki/The_Lostpedia_Interview:Sean_Douglas_Hoban |title=The Lostpedia Interview:Sean Douglas Hoban |work=Lostpedia |accessdate=2015-09-15 |archivedate=2015-09-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907053559/http://lostpedia.wikia.com/wiki/The_Lostpedia_Interview%3ASean_Douglas_Hoban |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

本集中的未来闪影镜头以本在撒哈拉沙漠中醒来开始，他的右臂受了伤，身穿[[达摩计划|达摩计划]]大衣，身上还散发出蒸汽。节目编剧专门给这种大衣起了代号<ref>{{cite news|last=Jensen |first=Jeff "Doc" |date=2008-04-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714180444/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20194903%2C00.html |archivedate=2014-07-14 |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2008/04/24/lost-s4-show-back |title='Lost' (S4): The show is back! |work=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2015-09-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。这段镜头中还存在多个[[彩蛋_(媒体)|彩蛋]]<ref>{{cite web | last = Kubicke | first = John | date = 2008-04-25 | title = ''Lost'' Easter Eggs: 'The Shape of Things to Come' #2—Teleportation in Tunisia | publisher = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2015-09-15 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714151040/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-easter-eggs-the-shape-of-18912.aspx | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-easter-eggs-the-shape-of-18912.aspx}}</ref>：本所穿大衣上的标签表明这原是埃德加·哈利瓦克斯（{{lang|en|Edgar Halliwax}}，[[弗朗克西斯·周|弗朗克西斯·周]]饰）的大衣，上面还有达摩计划工作站“兰花”的标志，该工作站要到下集《回家真好》时才首度出现<ref>{{cite episode | credits = Lindelof, Damon (writer) & Cuse, Carlton (writer) & Williams, Stephen (director) | title = There's No Place Like Home | series = Lost  | network = ABC | number = 12 | season = 4 | airedate = 2008-05-15}}</ref>。另一个彩蛋在下一组镜头中出现，时间很短，本的假加拿大护照上用的别名叫迪安·莫里亚蒂（{{lang|en|Dean Moriarty}}），这本护照之前在《[[经济学家_(迷失)|经济学家]]》（{{lang|en|''The Economist''}}）中出现过<ref>{{cite episode | credits = Kitsis, Edward (writer) & Adam Horowitz(writer) & Bender, Jack (director) | title = The Economist | series = Lost  | network = ABC | number = 3 | season = 4 | airedate = 2008-02-14}}</ref>，这个名字则是[[杰克·凯鲁亚克|杰克·凯鲁亚克]]1951年小说《[[在路上|在路上]]》的核心人物<ref>{{cite news | last = Medley | first = Mark | date = 2008-04-25 | title = 'The Shape of Things to Come': ''Lost'' Season Four, Episode Nine Recap | newspaper = ''The National Post''}}</ref>。编剧们最常被问到的问题就是他们是否已经计划好了将来的剧情<ref>{{cite news|last=Lindelof |first=Damon |date=2007-05-09 |url=http://www.kuwaittimes.net/read_news.php?newsid=MTU5OTA2MTUzOQ== |title="Lost" finale will be aired in 2010 |newspaper=''Kuwait Times'' |accessdate=2012-02-08 |archivedate=2012-02-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120208011003/http://www.kuwaittimes.net/read_news.php?newsid=MTU5OTA2MTUzOQ%3D%3D }}</ref>，所以编剧也试着在剧情中加入有关将来节目的影射，上文所述的大衣便是如此，编剧可以在之后以此为证，证明他们早就对剧情发展有了打算<ref name="podcast" />。据导演[[杰克·本德|杰克·本德]]所说，这场戏是在夏威夷某采石场拍摄，由于剧情中需要演员骑马并使用枪支，而外景地的岩石又不适合拍摄这组镜头，因此剧组不得不另觅地点，本德则在前面用起重机开路<ref>{{cite journal | last = Jensen | first = Jeff "Doc" | date = 2008-04-27 | title = Doc Jensen on Set | journal = ''Entertainment Weekly''}}</ref>。爱默生表示，拍摄这场戏的外景地非常荒凉，他本以为摄制过程会很轻松，但实际情况恰恰相反，像个大杂烩一样，不但要打斗、骑马、讲外语，还要彈钢琴。这些都让他颇感措手不及，工作才两周就感觉需要放假休息<ref>{{cite news | last = Jensen | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150721194258/http://www.ew.com/article/2008/04/14/lost-secrets-set | first = Jeff "Doc" | date = 2008-04-10 | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2008/04/14/lost-secrets-set | title = 'Lost': Secrets from the set! | publisher = ''Entertainment Weekly'' | accessdate = 2015-09-15 | archivedate = 2015-07-21 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

== 反响 ==
[[File:Drew_Goddard.png|thumb]]

《未来世界》于2008年4月24日通过美国广播公司在美国首播，在此期间及之后5小时里一共有1207.5万美国观众收看<ref name="Seidman">{{cite web | last = Seidman | first = Robert | date = 2008-05-13 | accessdate = 2015-07-16 | url = http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2008/05/12/idol-greys-lost-housewives-and-the-office-lead-weekly-dvr-viewing/3728/ | title = ''Idol'', ''Grey's'', ''Lost'', ''Housewives'' and ''The Office'' Lead Weekly DVR Viewing | work = TV by the Numbers | archivedate = 2015-07-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150716190933/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2008/05/12/idol-greys-lost-housewives-and-the-office-lead-weekly-dvr-viewing/3728/ }}</ref>，在这周的电视节目中名列第14<ref>{{cite web | work = ABC Medianet | date = 2008-04-29 | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=042908_06 | title = Weekly Program Rankings | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140417065154/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=042908_06 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2014-04-17 | archivedate = 2014-04-17}}</ref>。如果加上首播7天后观看预录的人数，则这集的美国观众人数会升至1406.7万<ref name="Seidman" />，与6周前播映的剧集相比有所进步。节目通过[[CTV电视网|CTV电视网]]在加拿大首播期间吸引了144.3万观众<ref>{{cite web | work = BBM Canada | date = 2008-04-30 | url = http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat04212008.pdf | title = Top Programs: Total Canada (English) | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090326061743/http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat04212008.pdf | accessdate = 2009-03-26 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2009-03-26}}</ref>，但在澳大利亚则只有68.3万人收看<ref>{{cite web | work = Seven Network | date = 2008-05-02 | url = http://www.ebroadcast.com.au/enews/seven/Seven---Daily-Ratings-Report-020508.html | title = Daily Ratings Report | accessdate = 2008-12-09 | archivedate = 2008-12-09 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081209011811/http://www.ebroadcast.com.au/enews/seven/Seven---Daily-Ratings-Report-020508.html}}</ref>。不过，《迷失》这周也获得了《[[太阳先驱报|太阳先驱报]]》（{{lang|en|''Sun-Herald''}}）评选的两项“波吉奖”（{{lang|en|Bogie Awards}}，恶搞澳大利亚的{{link-en|洛基獎|Logie Awards}}）提名，分别是“最受低估”电视剧和“电视台最令人心神不宁节目奖”<ref>{{cite news | last = Dale | first = David | date = 2008-04-27 | url = http://blogs.sunherald.com.au/whoweare/archives/2008/04/triballogies.html | title = The Tribal Mind: The Envelopes Please | newspaper = ''The Sun-Herald'' | accessdate = 2012-03-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120322082347/http://blogs.sunherald.com.au/whoweare/archives/2008/04/triballogies.html | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-03-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Dale | first = David | date = 2008-03-16 | url = http://blogs.sunherald.com.au/whoweare/archives/2008/04/the_tribal_mind_66.html | title = The Bogies: You Be the Judge and Jury | newspaper = ''The Sun-Herald'' | accessdate = 2012-03-22 | archivedate = 2012-03-22 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120322082332/http://blogs.sunherald.com.au/whoweare/archives/2008/04/the_tribal_mind_66.html}}</ref>。

《[[圣地亚哥联合论坛报|圣地亚哥联合论坛报]]》（{{lang|en|''The San Diego Union-Tribune''}}）给予本集“{{lang|en|A}}+”的最高评价<ref name="signon">{{cite news | last = Peterson | first = Karla | date = 2008-04-25 | newspaper = ''The San Diego Union-Tribune'' | url = http://weblog.signonsandiego.com/tvtracker/archives/022567.html | title = Lost: The Shape of Things to Come | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120209015511/http://weblog.signonsandiego.com/tvtracker/archives/022567.html | accessdate = 2012-02-09 | archivedate = 2012-02-09 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。杰夫·詹森（{{lang|en|Jeff Jensen}}）在《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》发文，称《未来世界》将“极富营养的启示和涂着糖衣的阴谋诡计相结合”，组成又一集美味可口、结构紧密的节目，他还预测艾莉克斯遭处决的一幕即便是到2010年5月《迷失》全剧终后仍然能在所有剧集中排到非常高的位置<ref>{{cite news|last=Jensen |first=Jeff "Doc" |date=2008-04-25 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20195369_2,00.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140224203617/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20195369_2%2C00.html |title=Raiders of the 'Lost' Story Arc |work=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2014-02-24 |archivedate=2014-02-24 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。第4季的季终集《[[最美是家|最美是家]]》（{{lang|en|''There's No Place Like Home''}}）播映前，詹森把艾莉克斯被处决的镜头排在第4季最佳时刻的第2位<ref>{{cite news|last=Jensen |first=Jeff |date=2008-05-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114061019/http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0%2C%2C20202804_20462007%2C00.html |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,20202804_14,00.html |title=Best Moment #2 of Season 4: 'He Changed the Rules |work=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2012-11-14 |archivedate=2012-11-14 }}</ref>，还把黑烟怪物攻击雇佣兵一幕排在第9名<ref>{{cite news|last=Jensen |first=Jeff |date=2008-05-29 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-11-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114061019/http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0%2C%2C20202804_20462007%2C00.html |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,20202804_7,00.html |title=Best Moment #9 of Season 4: Smokey Smokes 'Em |work=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2012-11-14 }}</ref>。《[[纽约_(杂志)|纽约]]》（{{lang|en|''New York''}}）杂志的丹·科伊斯（{{lang|en|Dan Kois}}）和莱恩·布朗（{{lang|en|Lane Brown}}）认为，这集在节奏上并不像以往的大部分《迷失》剧集那样平稳适中，剧情以揭密为导向，反倒感觉像是[[动作片|动作电影]]……就像岛上的《[[终极警探|终极警探]]》”<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Kois | first1 = Dan | last2 = Brown | first2 = Lois | date = 2008-04-25 | url = http://www.vulture.com/2008/04/lost_die_hard_on_an_island.html | title = ''Lost'': ''Die Hard'' on an Island | work = ''New York'' | accessdate = 2015-09-15 | archivedate = 2014-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140304195825/http://www.vulture.com/2008/04/lost_die_hard_on_an_island.html}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[IGN|IGN]]}}网站的克里斯·卡拉博特（{{lang|en|Chris Carabott}}）给予本集的评分为9.3（最高为10）<ref name="ign">{{cite web | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | last = Carabott | first = Chris | date = 2008-04-25 | publisher = IGN | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/04/25/lost-the-shape-of-things-to-come-review?page=2 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140301180123/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/04/25/lost-the-shape-of-things-to-come-review?page=2 | title = Lost: "The Shape of Things to Come" Review | archivedate = 2014-03-01}}</ref>，认为《未来世界》在各方面的品质都可以达到观众期望，他还特别称赞剧中艾莉克斯被杀的镜头直截了当得令人目瞪口呆，有可能会是《迷失》中最令人难忘、同时也至关重要的场景之一，观众看到这里很难会不为本感到难过<ref>{{cite web | last = Carabott | first = Chris | date = 2008-04-25 | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/04/25/lost-the-shape-of-things-to-come-review | title = Ben is Faced with an Unimaginable Decision | publisher = IGN | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140925121100/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/04/25/lost-the-shape-of-things-to-come-review | archivedate = 2014-09-25}}</ref>。{{lang|en|IGN}}还在评选《迷失》前5季的最佳剧集时把这集排在第2位，比评价甚佳的《[[透过窥镜|透过窥镜]]》和《[[試播_(迷失)|试播集]]》都高，仅次于《[[常量_(迷失)|常量]]》（{{lang|en|''The Constant''}}）<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141113040115/http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/12/09/igns-top-10-lost-episodes?page=2 | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/12/09/igns-top-10-lost-episodes?page=2 | title = IGN's Top 10 Lost Episodes | last1 = Fowler | first1 = Jeff | last2 = Goldman | first2 = Eric | last3 = Pirello | first3 = Phil | date = 2009-12-09 | publisher = IGN | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | archivedate = 2014-11-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[美国在线|美国在线]]电视小队的艾琳·马特尔（{{lang|en|Erin Martell}}）总结认为《未来世界》是表现辉煌的一集，其中不但有大量动作场面、多个重要解密，还留下更多的问题给观众思考<ref name="aol">{{cite web | last = Martell | first = Erin | date = 2008-04-24 | accessdate = 2011-05-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110521150929/http://www.tvsquad.com/2008/04/24/lost-the-shape-of-things-to-come/ | url = http://www.tvsquad.com/2008/04/24/lost-the-shape-of-things-to-come | title = Lost: The Shape of Things to Come | work = TV Squad | archivedate = 2011-05-21 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[BuddyTV|BuddyTV]]}}网站的唐·威廉姆斯（{{lang|en|Don Williams}}）认为，本集让之前5个星期的等待物有所值，并且其信息量是如此庞大，他觉得自己甚至需要给大脑一点时间放松<ref>{{cite web | last = Williams | first = Don | date = 2008-04-24 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-episode-49-the-shape-of-t-18863.aspx | title = Lost: Episode 4.9 "The Shape of Things to Come" Live Thoughts | publisher = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2015-09-16 |deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140226160020/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-episode-49-the-shape-of-t-18863.aspx | archivedate = 2014-02-26}}</ref>。威廉姆斯的同事奥斯卡·达尔（{{lang|en|Oscar Dahl}}）在评选第4季最佳瞬间时把艾莉克斯被杀排在第5名，称这一镜头有着“完美的节奏……令人极其震惊……能够侪身你所看过最完美的演出之列”<ref>{{cite web | last = Dahl | first = Oscar | date = 2008-06-02 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/more/5-moment-keamy-kills-alex-20082.aspx | title = Top Season 4 Moment #5: Keamy Kills Alex | publisher = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140226153212/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/more/5-moment-keamy-kills-alex-20082.aspx | archivedate = 2014-02-26}}</ref>。杰伊·格拉特菲尔特（{{lang|en|Jay Glatfelter}}）在《[[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]]》发文称，在带领观众重返《迷失》方面，《未来世界》的表现堪称完美。节目在发人深省上不及《常量》，但在惊险刺激的程度上却能和《试播集》的夸张和宏伟相提并论。<ref>{{cite news | last = Glatfelter | first = Jay | date = 2008-04-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150822085057/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/jay-glatfelter/on-ilosti-the-shape-of-th_b_98676.html | url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/jay-glatfelter/on-ilosti-the-shape-of-th_b_98676.html | title = On ''Lost'': "The Shape of Things to Come" | newspaper = [[赫芬顿邮报|The Huffington Post]] | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-08-22}}</ref>

《[[明星纪事报|明星纪事报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Star-Ledger''}}）的艾伦·塞平沃尔（{{lang|en|Alan Sepinwall}}）给予本集高度评价，称赞其中大量的动作戏和阴谋诡机，仿佛“（编剧）大罢工后来自天堂的甘露”，不过，他也批评剧中让3个临时演员扮演的815航班幸存者死亡，但主要角色却都平安无事的剧情设定，称“索耶躲避子弹的镜头本应给人紧张激烈的感觉，但实际上却只让人觉得好笑。”<ref name="nj">{{cite news | last = Sepinwall | first = Alan | date = 2008-04-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120210040639/http://blog.nj.com/alltv/2008/04/lost_the_shape_of_things_to_co.html | deadurl = no | url = http://blog.nj.com/alltv/2008/04/lost_the_shape_of_things_to_co.html | title = Lost, "The Shape of Things To Come": Smokey and the bandits | newspaper = ''The Star-Ledger'' | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | archivedate = 2012-02-10}}</ref>{{lang|en|[[E!|E!]]}}频道的[[克里斯汀·多斯·桑托斯|克里斯汀·多斯·桑托斯]]（{{lang|en|Kristin Dos Santos}}）对索耶躲开子弹的桥段也有同样看法<ref>{{cite web | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | last = Dos Santos | first = Kristin | date = 2008-04-25 | publisher = E! | url = http://www.eonline.com/news/4281/lost-redux-if-you-re-not-a-series-regular-get-back-inside | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080802153224/http://www.eonline.com/gossip/kristin/detail/index.jsp?uuid=db22eedc-686f-4003-a17b-dcc35e1084ed | title = ''Lost'' Redux: If You're Not a Series Regular, Get Back Inside! | archivedate = 2008-08-02}}</ref>。《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》周刊的杰米·波内沃兹克（{{lang|en|Jamie Poniewozik}}）在看到威德摩尔突然成为大反派，而本则开始满世界找他报仇的情节后对节目的发展方向感到忧虑，“看起来有些太像《[[双面女间谍|双面女间谍]]》”，但他总体上还是很喜欢这集在岛上的剧情<ref name="time">{{cite news|last=Poniewozik |first=James |date=2008-04-25 |url=http://www.time-blog.com/tuned_in/2008/04/lostwatch_a_game_of_risk.html |title=Lostwatch: A Game of Risk |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080429013436/http://www.time-blog.com/tuned_in/2008/04/lostwatch_a_game_of_risk.html |work=''[[时代_(杂志)|Time]]'' |archivedate=2008-04-29 |accessdate=2008-04-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[TMZ|TMZ]]}}网站的丹尼尔（{{lang|en|Daniel}}）对《未来世界》的评级为“{{lang|en|B}}”（最高为“{{lang|en|A}}”），称这是《迷失》表现坚实的又一集节目，在他看来，虽然节目始终没有让他有那种惊叫“我的天呐！”的时刻，但他整体上还是很满意，而且也很喜欢剧中艾莉克斯被处决的戏码<ref>{{cite web | author = Daniel | date = 2008-04-25 | url = http://www.tmz.com/2008/04/25/lost-diary-the-shape-of-things-to-come | archivedate = 2012-10-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121009010225/http://www.tmz.com/2008/04/25/lost-diary-the-shape-of-things-to-come/ | title = "Lost" Diary -- The Shape of Things to Come | work = [[TMZ|TMZ]] | accessdate = 2015-09-16}}</ref>。

由于剧本中有足够的发挥空间，迈克尔·爱默生在开拍前就决定以自己在这集里的演出参与[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]剧情类男配角奖角逐<ref>{{cite news | last = Nichols | first = Katherine | date = 2008-04-22 | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150907023102/http://archives.starbulletin.com/2008/04/22/features/story03.html | deadurl = no | url = http://archives.starbulletin.com/2008/04/22/features/story03.html | title = No Acting Required as Peril Looms | newspaper = ''Honolulu Star-Bulletin'' | archivedate = 2015-09-07}}</ref>。他顺利获得提名，这也是他凭同一角色连续第2次获提名，但最终不敌出演{{lang|en|[[FX_(电视频道)|FX]]}}频道电视剧《[[裂痕_(电视剧)|裂痕]]》的[[泽利科·伊万内克|泽利科·伊万内克]]（{{lang|en|Željko Ivanek}}）。不过，爱默生会在一年后凭《[[死者已死|死者已死]]》（{{lang|en|''Dead is Dead''}}）获奖。凯文·汤普森（{{lang|en|Kevin Thompson}}）在《[[棕榈滩邮报|棕榈滩邮报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Palm Beach Post''}}）发文指出，爱默生的“眼睛非常出戏，一个长时间的眼神甚至能表达出超过20页对白的内容……他再度证明，自己才是《迷失》中的明星、核心和灵魂，理应得到艾美奖的肯定。”<ref>{{cite news | last = Thompson | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | first = Kevin | date = 2008-04-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120518230601/http://www.palmbeachpost.com/blogs/content/shared-blogs/palmbeach/thompson/entries/2008/04/if_michael_emer.html | title = The Night Belongs To Big Ben | newspaper = ''The Palm Beach Post'' | url = http://www.palmbeachpost.com/blogs/content/shared-blogs/palmbeach/thompson/entries/2008/04/if_michael_emer.html | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-05-18}}</ref>{{lang|en|E!}}频道的珍妮弗·戈德温（{{lang|en|Jennifer Godwin}}）表示，在展现[[超级坏蛋|超级坏蛋]]人性化一面上，爱默生的表现无人能出其右<ref>{{cite web | last = Godwin | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | first = Jennifer | date = 2008-04-25 | url = http://www.eonline.com/news/8848/death-dear-ones-and-the-monster-michael-emerson-talks-lost | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080802151642/http://www.eonline.com/gossip/kristin/detail/index.jsp?uuid=8238465c-26fb-4a93-9fa4-629af9f8b05c | title = Death, Dear Ones and the Monster: Michael Emerson Talks ''Lost'' | publisher = E! | archivedate = 2008-08-02}}</ref>。除此以外，《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》的罗伯特·比安科（{{lang|en|Robert Bianco}}）<ref>{{cite news | last = Bianco | first = Robert | date = 2008-06-12 | title = Who Will Make Emmy Happy? | work = ''[[今日美国|USA Today]]'' | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/televisionawards/emmys/2008-06-12-emmy-ballot_N.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021013818/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/televisionawards/emmys/2008-06-12-emmy-ballot_N.htm | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，《[[电视指南_(美国杂志)|电视指南]]》的马特·劳什（{{lang|en|Matt Roush}}）<ref>{{cite web | last = Roush | first = Matt | date = 2008-04-25 | accessdate = 2008-07-18 | url = http://community.tvguide.com/blog-entry/TVGuide-Editors-Blog/Roush-Dispatch/Battlestar-Galactica-Met/800038315 | title = Week in Review: 20 Unforgettable Moments | work = ''[[电视指南_(美国杂志)|TV Guide]]'' | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080718063234/http://community.tvguide.com/blog-entry/TVGuide-Editors-Blog/Roush-Dispatch/Battlestar-Galactica-Met/800038315 | archivedate = 2008-07-18}}</ref>、《[[数码间谍|数码间谍]]》的本·劳森-琼斯（{{lang|en|Ben Rawson-Jones}}，他还给予《未来世界》最高的5星评级）<ref>{{cite web | last = Rawson-Jones | first = Ben | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140716025000/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/ustv/s10/lost/review/a95276/s04e09-the-shape-of-things-to-come.html | work = [[数码间谍|Digital Spy]] | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | date = 2008-05-04 | archivedate = 2014-07-16 | url = http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/ustv/s10/lost/review/a95276/s04e09-the-shape-of-things-to-come.html | title = S04E09: 'The Shape Of Things To Come'}}</ref>、{{lang|en|BuddyTV}}的约翰·库比西克（{{lang|en|John Kubicek}}）<ref>{{cite web | last = Kubicek | publisher = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2015-09-16 | first = John | date = 2008-04-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714151040/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-easter-eggs-the-shape-of-18912.aspx | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-easter-eggs-the-shape-of-18912.aspx | title = Lost Easter Eggs: "The Shape of Things to Come" | archivedate = 2014-07-14}}</ref>，以及前文所述，分别来自《明星纪事报》<ref name="nj" />、《圣地亚哥联合论坛报》<ref name="signon" />、《时代》周刊<ref name="time" />、《娱乐周刊》<ref name="ew" />、{{lang|en|IGN}}<ref name="ign" />和电视小队的评论家都对爱默生饰演的本有高度评价<ref name="aol" />。

